name: Tim Caldwell
text: Sawgrass is the absolute best in surveying and engineering consultants in Baldwin County and the greater Mobile area!!!  Excellent work,  excellent quality, excellent prices!!!

name: Misty Fontenot
text: I work for an architecture firm in Birmingham and part of my job is to secure surveys for our clients that we use to begin work with them. I work closely with the Gonzalez-Strength team and they are all so wonderful. They are incredibly responsive and do excellent land surveys. We’ve done multiple jobs with them so far and look forward to our continued relationship!

name: Perry Barbaree
text: I'm a real estate agent in Bham area.  I have worked with GSA many times, personally and professionally.  They are responsive, nice, professional and competitively priced.  If you need a survey or Engineering services, choose this group.

resp.text: Perry, we appreciate the great review and absolutely enjoy working with you!  Thanks so much!

name: Kevin Stober
text: Best Civil Engineering & Survey Co. to work for. We pride ourselves in not only doing an excellent job but to make our clients happy knowing it's done right.
